---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const frontmatter = {
  title: "The Vision",
  description: "Closing the gap between human sparks and production reality.",
  quote: "Turning ideas into life is not a technical challenge‚Äîit's a pursuit of meaning."
};
---

<PageLayout frontmatter={frontmatter}>
  <p class="mb-16 text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-white/90">
    Most ideas disappear before they are ever felt. The journey from <span class="text-white font-bold">Concept</span> to <span class="text-white font-bold">Product</span> is often fragmented, slow, and limited by the tools we use. We believe that Generative AI is the bridge that can finally close this gap.
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-32">
    <!-- Why We Explore Section -->
    <section>
       <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-12 flex items-center gap-4">
        <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-accent-blue/50"></span>
        Why we explore
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-6">‚ú®</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Tangibility</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            What if a simple human idea could become a tangible experience in minutes?
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-6">ü§ù</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Collaboration</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            How do we design AI systems that feel like collaborators, not just tools?
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-6">üíô</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Trust</h3>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Can we build AI experiences that people deeply trust and love to use?
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-6">
         <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-white flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-accent-violet/50"></span>
          Beyond the Demos
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-white/70">
          We are not here to build novelty. We are here to architect the future of human-AI synergy‚Äîtransforming raw intuition into production-ready digital reality.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-white/70">
          This studio is the home for the experiments, the failures, and the breakthroughs that matter.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-accent-blue/20 to-accent-violet/20 rounded-3xl blur-2xl group-hover:blur-3xl transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-black/40 border border-white/10 p-10 rounded-3xl backdrop-blur-md">
           <span class="font-display text-6xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-blue to-accent-violet opacity-30">
             Build.
           </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Studio Path Section -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-12 flex items-center gap-4">
        <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-accent-sunset/50"></span>
        The Studio Path
      </h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:bg-accent-blue/10 group-hover:border-accent-blue/30 transition-all">
            <span class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-white/50 group-hover:text-accent-blue">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-accent-blue transition-colors">Intention First</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">We start with a human problem, not a feature list. Technology serves the intent, never the other way around.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:bg-accent-violet/10 group-hover:border-accent-violet/30 transition-all">
             <span class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-white/50 group-hover:text-accent-violet">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-accent-violet transition-colors">Agentic Mastery</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">We orchestrate specialized AI agents to act as craftsmen, each an expert in their domain, working in concert.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:bg-accent-sunset/10 group-hover:border-accent-sunset/30 transition-all">
             <span class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-white/50 group-hover:text-accent-sunset">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-accent-sunset transition-colors">Rapid Evolution</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">We ship prototypes early, listen to the loop, and refine with intent. Perfection is found in the iteration.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
